I""<h2 id="find-texture-locations-im-materialx-image-vops">Find Texture Locations im materialX Image VOPs</h2>
<p>Useful for when you have a large scene that is returning missing texture references but you don’t know where.</p>

<p>’’’
import hou
import os</p>

<p>texture = hou.ui.readInput(message=”Texture Name.ext”)</p>

<p>nodes = hou.vopNodeTypeCategory().nodeType(“mtlximage”).instances()</p>

<p>for node in nodes:
    if os.path.basename(node.parm(“file”).eval()) == texture[1]:
        print(node.path())
‘’’</p>
